    "1.16.3-1.0.34": "Some breaking changes to the block and item tag providers. They use the setup layout now like any other libx base provider. This should not be a problem to end users as the classes are only used during datagen. Also some more utility functions for the recipe provider base - noeppi_noeppi",
    "1.16.3-1.0.35": "This will give a duplicate version on curse but I really need to remove the tab characters now. - noeppi_noeppi",
