    "1.16.3-1.0.38": "Make it possible to have prefixes in RegisterClass annotations to avoid duplicates and keep field names simple. - noeppi_noeppi",
    "1.16.3-1.0.39": "Change the maven location back - noeppi_noeppi\nAdd a new loot entry type that can select multiple items from its children in one entry. This allows for much more complex loot tables. - noeppi_noeppi",
